<p>A peaceful theme for Jekyll and GitHub Pages.</p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Optimized for Chinese/Japanese/English languages</li>
  <li>Full compatibility with GitHub Pages</li>
  <li><code>.sidenote</code> elements</li>
  <li>Iconic social media links with font-awesome (size optimized)</li>
  <li>Support retina images</li>
  <li>Cross browser support (supports all modern browsers)</li>
  <li>Google Analytics and Disqus integration</li>
  <li>Customizable syntax highlighting color scheme</li>
</ul>

<p>Visit <a href="https://github.com/kamikat/jekyll-theme-kagami">project homepage</a> for instructions on installation
and configuration.</p>

